'''Taswast Tamaziɣt''' d [[taswast]] [[Takerza|tanekrazt]] yettusxedmen deg tmura n [[Tafriqt n ugafa|Tefriqt n ugafa]] (ɣer [[imaziɣen]] d [[imaziɣen imserɣnen]] tikwal). Taswast Tamaziɣt d tin yezwaren [[taswast tagrigurt]] s 950 n [[aseggas|yiseggasen]]. [[Ass]] amenzu n teswast-a ([[Yennayer]]) yettmagar-d ass n [[12 te]] seg [[taswast tagrigurt|teswast tagrigurt]].

== Tiswasin tizikanin == 
Kra kan n yisalan i yellan ɣef beṭṭu n [[akud|wakud]] ɣer [[imaziɣen|yimaziɣen]] n zik. Kra n yiferdisen n yiwet n teswast [[azarnslem|tazarneslemt]] u ahat daɣen tazar-ṛumant deg kra n yidlisen n [[tallit talemmast]] i yeɣra [[Van den Boogert]] (2002) mmalen-d agazen yezdin yakk d teswast n [[Imuhaɣ|yimuhaɣ]] tamensayt akken i d-mmalen d akken tella teswast yettusxedmen di talliyin timzikin (tiqburin) gar n yimuhaɣ n zik.


